    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵחֲבֵירָיו; אוֹ הֲלָכָה <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">כְּרַבִּי</span> מֵחֲבֵירוֹ – וַאֲפִילּוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵחֲבֵירָיו. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2285\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רב נחמן בר יעקב\">רַב נַחְמָן</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"of Rav, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רַב</span>: אָסוּר לַעֲשׂוֹת",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּדִבְרֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">רַבִּי</span>. קָא סָבַר: הֲלָכָה <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">כְּרַבִּי</span> מֵחֲבֵירוֹ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְלֹא מֵחֲבֵירָיו. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2285\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רב נחמן בר יעקב\">וְרַב נַחְמָן</span> דִּידֵיהּ אָמַר: מוּתָּר",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לַעֲשׂוֹת כְּדִבְרֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">רַבִּי</span>. קָא סָבַר: הֲלָכָה <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi, sixth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1508\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda HaNasi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה הנשיא\">כְּרַבִּי</span> מֵחֲבֵירוֹ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וַאֲפִילּוּ מֵחֲבֵירָיו. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span>: אָסוּר",
      "segment_ids": [
